programme.desc: Mizan dan Hani semakin mesra, Hani menunaikan tanggungjawab sebagai suri rumah, tetapi mereka masih tidak bersama sebagai suami isteri ketika di kamar. Nizam yang menelefon Hani tidak dijawabnya, sebaliknya Sheila pula yang memanggilnya lalu Nizam marahkan Sheila, malahan bertegas yang Hani tetap mencintainya. Ini membuatkan Sheila berubah kelakuan dan marah-marah bersendirian terhadap Hani. Suraya masih dengan cara hidupnya, kali ini dia ke Langkawi untuk menemui seorang lelaki lain dan dia tidak perasan Nizam ternampaknya. Hani terus berbaik-baik dengan Sarah dan Yusri. Sekian lama tidak melawati ke rumah mereka, selain menemui Sarah, Hani juga membeli sebuah motorsikal baru kepada Yusri. Itu pun setelah Hani mendapat kebenaran keluar rumah daripada Mizan. Mizan dan Hani juga keluar makan bersama dan semasa perjalanan Mizan menasihati Hani berusaha mendapat kerjaya yang sesuai dan membuat persiapan dan Hani mendengar serta akur. Mizan di pejabat secara tidak langsung telah memaklumkan dia telah berkahwin dan di cari oleh ibunya dan jika sesuai nanti dia akan mengenalkan kepada Sharif dan Dzul kerana mereka sering berharap kerana sebagai rakan. Manakala Sharif meminta Mak ciknya yang biasa denganya agar menguruskan dia untuk berkenalan dengan seorang wanita bernama Hani

Aidil terdiam dan menyuruh Zahlia berubah dan menerima cinta Zahirin yang benar-benar ikhlas terhadapnya. Dia sedar yang dia sebenarnya perlukan Zahirin dan dia setuju berkahwin dengan Zahirin. programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep12
programme.desc: Hani dengan tanpa kebenaran suaminya telah menghubungi Nizam dan ini diketahui Mizan. Sebenarnya Hani amat menyayangi ibu mentuanya yang mengharapkan Hanilah yang dapat memujuk Nizam. Sebenarnya perbualan Hani dan Nizam semata-mata mengharap Nizam balik berjumpa ibu dan Sheila. malahan dalam perbualan dia meminta Nizam lupakan sahaja kisah mereka. Dia juga bertegas ketaatsetianya hanyalah kepada suaminya. Berikutan itu Nizam anggapkan Hani tidak lagi sukakannya. Dalam pada itu Mizan yang tidak tahu sepenuhnya bualan Hani terus andaikan isterinya masih sukakan Nizam. Mizan berubah tingkah laku dan kemudiannya disedari Hani punca daripadanya. Hani cuba meminta maaf dan ingin menjelaskan kedudukan sebenar. Mizan masih marah dan cemburu tanpa usul periksa. Kebetulan Mizan terlihat lukisan-lukisan Hani, dari lukisan jelas yang Hani benar-benar cinta dan sukakannya. Mizan dan Hani saling maaf bermaafan selepas itu dan Mizan langsung tidak mencurigai, malahan hubungan mereka kini lebih mesra. Mizan juga amat ceria ke pejabat hingga menghairankan rakan sekerja. Suraya di Langkawi kebetulan bertemu Nizam. Nizam tahu Suraya masih mahukan abangnya, justeru dengan gambar-gambar aktiviti sosial Suraya yang ada, Nizam seolah-olah mengugut Suraya. Nizam mahukan Suraya dapat berperanan untuk mengeruhkan perhubungan Mizan dengan isterinya sehingga mereka bercerai.

programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep07
programme.desc: Memaparkan hubungan Melissa dengan Syakir baik sebagai suami isteri cuma mereka tidak tidur di bilik yang sama. Bukanlah akibat sesuatu tetapi Melissa sendiri masih kekok, dia masih memanggil tuan Syak kepada suaminya. Dia berbahasa begitu kerana Syakir adalah bosnya ketika bekerja di book cafe. Melissa berat untuk meninggalkan pekerjaannya tetapi atas permintaan suaminya dia sanggup berbuat begitu. Jenny majikannya pun agak berat untuk melepaskan tetapi kerana permintaan Syakir, dia tiada pilihan. Syakir membawa Melissa ke rumah baru. Melissa terkejut kerana rumah barunya ini lebih besar dan memerlukan tenaga kerja yang lebih. Atas sebab itu Syakir meminta Melissa untuk berhenti kerja dan menumpukan sepenuh perhatian sebagai suri rumah tangga. Mereka sentiasa bersama mengemas rumah, Syakir kelihatan puas hati tindak tanduk Melissa. Pelbagai kejadian lucu dan romantik yang berlaku sepanjang mereka berada di rumah tersebut. Syakir dan Melissa belajar untuk mengenali diri masing-masing di rumah tersebut kerana banyak masa yang mereka habiskan bersama. Suatu hari mereka ke pasaraya, di suatu ketika Syakir tertinggal satu barang di kaunter, ketika Melissa berdiri berseorangan Zamer ternampaknya dari jauh, dia cuba untuk ke situ, tiba-tiba datang Syakir semula dan mereka berjalan sama. Ini telah menghairankan Zamer dengan merungut Melissa masih bersama lelaki yang sama. Sementara itu Shamsul yang berbincang dengan Syakir tentang projek perniagaan bapanya yang mana dia kini perlu mengetua di bahagian akitek dalam satu projek baru. Di suatu ketika ibu Melissa tidak sihat, Melissa meminta izin balik menemui ibunya. Melissa tahu suaminya sibuk bekerja dan dia hanya memadai Syakir hantar ke stesen bas. Tiba di kampung Melissa jadi takut untuk menghubungi Syakir membuatkan Syakir tertunggu, bimbang dan sebagainya. Shamsul datang bersantai di bilik Syakir dan dia mendapati Syakir tidak bersemangat. Syakir akui dia terasa bosan pun ada, duduk rumah tidak kena dan duduk di pejabat pun tidak kena. Dari cerita Syakir Shamsul merujuk kepada pengalaman sama dia pernah lalui ketika dia berpisah 2 bulan dengan Nora. Jadi terasa amat sangat api cinta itu. Syakir terdiam, apabila jikanya sebegitu Syakir ditanyakan dia rindukan kepada siapa. Cakap-cakap Shamsul terbawa-bawa Syakir semasa berseorangan di rumahnya. Melissa bercadang akan menghubungi suaminya, tiba-tiba pintu rumahnya diketuk dan Melissa hairan seseorang yang datang itu

Hani cuba meminta maaf dan ingin menjelaskan kedudukan sebenar. Mizan masih marah dan cemburu tanpa usul periksa. Kebetulan Mizan terlihat lukisan-lukisan Hani, dari lukisan jelas yang Hani benar-benar cinta dan sukakannya. Mizan dan Hani saling maaf bermaafan selepas itu dan Mizan langsung tidak mencurigai, malahan hubungan mereka kini lebih mesra. Mizan juga amat ceria ke pejabat hingga menghairankan rakan sekerja. Suraya di Langkawi kebetulan bertemu Nizam. Nizam tahu Suraya masih mahukan abangnya, justeru dengan gambar-gambar aktiviti sosial Suraya yang ada, Nizam seolah-olah mengugut Suraya. Nizam mahukan Suraya dapat berperanan untuk mengeruhkan perhubungan Mizan dengan isterinya sehingga mereka bercerai.

programme.desc: Mona tersedar di hospital dan mendapati dirinya mengandung. Badrul merayu Mona agar tidak berpisah. Kehadiran ibu bapanya menyebabkan Mona terpaksa menangguhkan keputusannya. Dr. Norma nampak keadaan Mona dan menawarkan diri untuk membantunya secara klinikal. Irfan dan Mimi berjaya menjejaki Sam dan mengetahui hubungan lelaki itu dengan Wani. Mereka semakin mengesyaki bahawa anak Wani itu ialah anak Sam. Badrul berterus terang bahawa dia tidak cintakan Wani. Apabila Wani terus mendesaknya, dia akhirnya mencabar Wani untuk menjalankan ujian DNA. Selepas menilai masalah Mona, Julia merasakan Mona terkena buatan orang dan cuba membawanya pergi berubat dengan seorang bomoh. Mimi tidak bersetuju dengan cara itu.

Mizan sebenarnya salah sangka kerana Hani di situ berbual dengan Atuk Yusri dan Sarah di bilik lain, sedangkan Yusri berada di tandas. Sangkaan Mizan Hani ada hubungan dengan Yusri. Berikutan itu Hani kecewa dan kecil hati dan merajuk. Mizan pula kini kesal dengan sikap dan sangkaannya. Tanpa di sangka Nizam datang ke rumah Mizan dan Mizan membenarkan Hani berbual dengan Nizam, tetapi Hani hanya bercakap dia sebagai suami Mizan dan nasihati Nizam jangan abaikan ibu dan bapanya. Sebelum itu Nizam berterus terang kepada Sheila dia pulang bukan kerananya tetapi disebabkan ibu dan bapanya. Shariff sejak di hari itu terus bergegas pulang setelah tahu status Hani.

programme.title: Dapur Bujang Western S2 Ep13
programme.desc: Hujung bulan? Poket kering? Bajet kecik tetapi selera besar? Jangan risau, dengan modal RM20.00, anda boleh menyediakan 2 jenis masakan western dengan cepat dan mudah. programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep08
programme.desc: Memaparkan agak tergamam Melissa yang tiba itu suaminya. Melissa susah hati rumah mereka hanya ada dua bilik, sebilik telah dihuni ibunya dan sebilik lagi Syakir minta dia berehat, sedangkan bilik itu khas untuknya. Syakir menerangkan tidak apa apa masalah mereka tinggal sebilik tetapi Melissa setuju yang dia akan tidur di bawah katil dengan alasan darjat suami perlu di jaga. Syakir tidak peduli dan bila balik ke Kuala Lumpur hendak tidur bersama pun boleh dan tidur berasingan pun ada bilik yang banyak. Di pejabat bapa Syakir bertanyakan tentang prestasi kerja Syakir kepada Shamsul. Shamsul mendapati kerjakerjanya semua selesai dan bapanya juga kelihatan dia sentiasa ceria dan kreatif dengan kerjanya. Cuma yang menghairankan Shamsul pun tidak tahu dia kemana kerana dia bercuti seminggu lagi. Bapanya menanyakan adakah Syakir sedang bercinta, Shamsul juga tidak tahu. Bapanya meminta agar Shamsul memantau adiknya itu, bimbang terjadi sesuatu kerana akhir-akhir ini dia banyak berahsia. Takut apa yang terjadi ibunya nanti buat kacau yang bukan-bukan pula. Shamsul hanya mengiakan. Semasa di rumah ibu Melissa, Melissa bersapa dengan "abang" sebagai tidak meragukan ibunya. Syakir dan Melissa saling merindui walaupun masing-masing tidak mahu mengakuinya. Walaupun sudah sah menjadi suami isteri, Melissa masih lagi menjaga auratnya di hadapan Syakir. Manakala di rumah Kamelia dia mendesak abangnya ingin tahu lokasi Syakir, sedangkan abangnya marah sikapnya opses masih mengejar Syakir. Sementara itu Nora, kakak ipar Syakir berada di wad kerana keguguran. Syakir yang dapat tahu berjanji akan balik ke Kuala Lumpur. Shamsul sebenarnya berkawan baik dengan Engku Razi, dia berkongsi masalah yang dihadapi dan Engku Razi simpati. Engku Razi memberitahu hal Nora kepada Engku kamelia. Engku Kamelia tidak kisah, apa yang mahu hanya Syakir bukan keluarga mereka. Melissa dan Syakir kini balik di rumah mereka, kemesraan semakin baik, tetapi Melissa masih takut-takut dan Syakir meminta Melissa jangan memanggilnya sebagai tuan Syak. Melissa juga memaklumkan ada surat untuk Syakir diterima. Dalam pada itu Zamer pula memandu membawa Engku Kamelia. Kamelia masuk ke dalam book cafe dan meminta Zamer jawab panggilan dan memegang sebentar tas tangannya. Semasa inilah ada panggilan daripada Syakir, Zamer tidak menjawab tetapi dia tertanya sendiri apakah pula hubungan Syakir ini dengan Kamelia

programme.title: Anggun Mikayla Ep05
programme.desc: Perjalanan hidup Mikayla sentiasa bersimpang-siur dengan dugaan sejak dia mencelikkan mata birunya ke dunia. Status kelahirannya membuatkan dia seringkali menerima cacian penduduk kampung dan menjadi mangsa buli semasa kecil. Mekap adalah cara Mikayla menidakkan kewujudannya sendiri. Dia berselindung di sebalik rambut palsu hitam untuk menyorokkan rambut auburnnya serta mengenakan pelbagai jenis mekap untuk menggelapkan warna kulit kerana keinginannya untuk tampak Melayu. Siang, Mikayla bekerja sebagai jurumekap artis dan apabila malam tiba, dia menjelma sebagai pontianak. Pertemuan Mikayla dengan Idriz dalam satu insiden lucu telah mencipta satu hubungan aneh yang tidak bernama. Dalam diam, Idriz menyimpan rasa tetapi keinginannya terbatas kerana tanggungjawabnya pada keluarga. Jurugambar yang bekerja bersamanya, Asif yang suka mengusik Mikayla mulai tersedar yang usikannya sudah bertukar menjadi perasaan sebenar. Tetapi, dia terlajak memikat pelakon popular bernama Andria, sebelum tersedar tentang perasaannya terhadap Mikayla. Sedang Mikayla dalam keadaan celaru, lelaki dari masa silamnya, Aidan pula muncul kembali, menagih kemaafan kerana meninggalkan parut panjang di dahinya. Aidan yang kini sudah bergelar pelakon popular cuba memadamkan kenangan sakit mereka demi merebut hati yang dirinduinya itu. Tetapi, impian Mikayla hanya satu, berhadapan dengan masa silamnya dan mencantas kebencian mama. Cinta bukan destinasi yang diimpi. Namun, hatinya terus menjadi buruan oleh tiga orang lelaki.

programme.title: rock bro
programme.desc: Rock Bro! diceritakan melalui naratif Jijoe, kemuncak pencapaian mereka apabila menjadi finalis Anugerah Juara Lagu, namun era rock mula meniti fasa kejatuhan dengan kemasukan aliran muzik rap dan hip-hop pada awal 90-an. Amy Mat Piah meninggalkan jawatan sebagai pengurus kumpulan Rimba Bara kerana keinginanya yang terlalu kuat untuk menjadi penyanyi Rock. Namun begitu,o kumpulan Rimba Bara tetap meneruskan perjuangan musik mereka..Rimba Bara menerima seorang pembantu bernama Dio. Pada ketika ini jemputan untuk membuat persembahan mula berkurang sehingga memaksa mereka melakukan kerja sambilan bagi menyara hidup, selain mengambil tawaran gig di tapak ekspo tani. Disaat ini hati Zul Kapan mula berbolak balik dek kerana kecewa dengan perjalanan musik kumpulan mereka. Pada ketika ini juga prestasi Black mula terjejas kerana penyakit misteri. Zul yang sudah mula bosan mengambil keputusan untuk meninggalkan dunia muzik dan melibatkan diri dengan aktiviti agama.

Ain terasa namun dia lagi terasa bila semua orang asyik back up Aidil dan bukan dirinya. Ini yang menambah marah di hati Ain. Dia merasakan semua orang sudah tidak sayang kepadanya. Sikit-sikit merajuk lari ke rumah Wahida. Aidil cuba menjadi suami yang terbaik dengan melayan perangai Ain yang pelik-pelik. Setiap hari ada sahaja yang tidak kena. Ada juga Aidil pernah mengeluh pada Adila namun kakaknya memberitahu yang sikap itu biasa untuk perempuan mengandung. Muaz juga nampaknya selalu menyebelahi Aidil kerana dia sendiri sihat Aidil bergegas ke sana ke mari demi menunaikan craving Ain. Ain pula dalam masa yang sama takut apabila melihat perutnya semakin membesar dan teringat akan janji-janjinya untuk berpisah bersama Aidil. Kadang-kadang dia kasihan apabila melihat sikap Aidil yang banyak berubah tetapi ada masanya dia tidak boleh melupakan apa yang Aidil pernah buat pada dirinya.

programme.desc: Semasa perang menentang komunis, seorang askar Thai mempertaruhkan nyawanya untuk menyelamatkan seorang budak lelaki Hmong dari sebuah perkampungan yang terbakar di utara. Budak itu membesar menjadi Kapten Songkiat, seorang askar yang berjanji setia kepada negara Thai.

programme.title: Den Budak Motor
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Deniel, seorang lelaki yang kecewa ditinggalkan oleh bekas kekasihnya, Sarah disebabkan kesusahan Deniel yang hanya memiliki motor kapcai.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep 7 Ep7
programme.desc: Ashikin dan Uzair kembali bersama tetapi Imran sedaya upaya mendapatkan Ashikin kembali. Rakan-rakan Uzair datang menyokong Uzair dan Ashikin. Uzair terkejut apabila Hatta datang berlawan dengannya menentang Imran. Mereka cuba melarikan diri dari bandar tetapi Imran menggunakan Ajeeb mempunyai umpan.

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep 11 Ep11
programme.desc: Nina mendengar bacaan mantra datang dari bilik Echa. Apabila Nina menjenguk Echa terus histeria. Halim dan Nina membawa Echa pergi ke rumah Dawami setelah gagal dihubungi. Dipertengahan jalan, Echa merota dan melompar keluar dari kenderaan. Kebetulan Mat berada di tempat itu terus menyelamatkakn Echa dari dilanggar. Halim, Nina, Echa dan Mat pergi ke rumah Dawami untuk berubat Echa. Echa berjaya dipulih, sekaligus membuka dalang santau yang mengenai Nina. Mat dan Dawami mentarbiah Halim dan Nina supaya kembali ke jalan Allah.

programme.title: Cadaver
programme.desc: Seon-hwa ialah pelajar baharu di sekolah perubatan elit, dan dia dimulakan ke kelas pembedahan yang diketuai oleh Dr. Han bersama lima pelajar lain, termasuk teman lelakinya Ki-beom. Selepas kelas pertama semua pelajar mula berkongsi mimpi ngeri yang sama melibatkan seorang pakar bedah bermata satu, dan satu demi satu mereka mula dibunuh, mangsa ditemui dengan hati mereka dikeluarkan. Seon-hwa dan Ki-beom yakin bahawa peristiwa ini berkaitan dengan mayat yang cantik dengan tatu mawar di payudaranya, dan mereka memulakan penyiasatan untuk mendedahkan identitinya.

programme.title: Interchange
programme.desc: Dihantui oleh penglihatan yang suram, jurugambar forensik Adam berundur dari dunia, tinggal di rumah dan mengambil gambar jirannya sehingga dia diseret ke dalam penyiasatan lain oleh kawan baiknya, Detektif Man, yang meminta bantuannya untuk menyelesaikan siri pembunuhan ritual yang mengerikan. Pada masa yang sama, hobi Adam yang kelihatan tidak berbahaya tidak lama kemudian menjadi lebih gelap apabila dia mengintip Iva, seorang wanita muda dari Borneo. Terpesona olehnya, dia tidak lama lagi terjerat dalam rangkaian misteri dan pembunuhannya. Ketika Adam diseret lebih jauh ke dalam dunia puak Iva dan Man menyelidiki penyiasatannya dengan lebih mendalam, mereka menemui mistik bawah tanah bomoh dan makhluk ghaib di bandar itu.

programme.title: Superbike
programme.desc: Ia berkisar tentang kehidupan seharian sekumpulan penunggang motosikal superbike yang menggelar kumpulan mereka sebagai 'Pirate Bikers' dan diketuai oleh Bugs (Kamal Adli). Berlumba-lumba di jalanan, kejar-mengejar, berkonvoi dan disaman oleh polis telah menjadi rasa masam dalam kehidupan mereka yang berkongsi minat yang sama.

programme.title: Encounter
programme.desc: Sekumpulan rakan mendedahkan objek dunia lain di padang luar bandar yang mereka temui menyimpan rahsia yang lebih besar daripada yang mereka bayangkan.

programme.desc: Kisah pahlawan Tien, yang telah ditangkap oleh panglima perang yang kejam Tuan Rajasena. Tien melarikan diri daripada cengkaman Rajasena, pulih daripada kecederaannya yang melumpuhkan dengan bantuan Guru Bua, dan kembali untuk berhadapan dengan Bhuti Sangkha, yang telah menggantikan Rajasena sebagai penjahat utama.

programme.title: The Invoking
programme.desc: Selepas mewarisi rumah daripada keluarga yang tidak pernah dikenalinya, Samantha Harris (Trin Miller) dan tiga rakannya menuju ke Sader Ridge luar bandar untuk memeriksa harta itu. Tidak lama selepas tiba, Sam mula mengalami penglihatan mengerikan tentang kekejaman ganas dan kejahatan yang tidak terkata. Diganggu oleh kuasa jahat yang mengepungnya, Sam mengalami mimpi ngeri apabila syaitan dari masa lalunya enggan terus dikebumikan lagi.

programme.desc: Satu siri kematian dan kehilangan kejam membawa kembali kepada legenda bandar tentang badut pembunuh bersiri. Sekumpulan pelajar kolej akan menghadapi mimpi ngeri terburuk mereka, apabila Badut jahat ini kembali dari masa lalu pada Halloween.

programme.desc: Sekumpulan pencuri yang menggelarkan diri mereka sebagai Geng Santa Claus sedang menimbulkan kekacauan, dan polis tidak dapat mengejarnya. Kapten polis Gilbert terganggu oleh seorang wartawan Cina yang menulis cerita tentang skuadnya, isteri detektif Emilien baru sahaja mengumumkan bahawa dia hamil, dan pemandu teksi Daniel sedang mengalami krisis hubungan. Selepas rentetan kesilapan di mana pencuri mengakali polis berkali-kali dengan wartawan di sana untuk merakam semuanya, Daniel dan teksi supernya masuk.

Berbekalkan ajaran Pak Hassan, Fikri pulang ke rumah lamanya tetapi dia terpaksa berdepan dengan abangnya Ali, yang menyembunyikan rahsia gelap misteri di sebalik ancaman Makhluk di dalam almari.

programme.desc: Desta dilahirkan dalam keluarga bahagia. Namun, kebahagiaan dalam keluarga tidak kekal lama apabila hantaran sihir membawa kepada kematian kedua ibu bapa. Desta membesar menjadi seorang yang menyendiri dan penuh misteri. Keinginannya untuk membalas dendam membuatkan dia mencari dalang di sebalik kematian ibu bapanya.

programme.desc: Semasa memburu haiwan, Wittaya dan Lokrai secara tidak sengaja menyinggung perasaan Nang Ta-Kian, roh penjaga hutan, yang kemudian membunuh Lokrai. Wittaya terpaksa menjaga anak kawannya, Tong Kam. Sebagai seorang lelaki muda, Tong Kam jatuh cinta dengan anak perempuan Wittaya, Porn tetapi Wittaya lebih suka Trai, seorang jurutera awam yang datang ke kampung mereka untuk menyelaraskan pembinaan empangan. Shasa hanya menyatakan kerana Nia terbawa-bawa dan memikirkan yang dia alami. Sementara itu, Pak Abas dan Roslan bercakap tentang arwah Rosserita. Di pejabat, Nia diganggui oleh saka Gelam. Dia perasan bahawa pembantu rumahnya, Bella telah hilang. Bella seperti adik kepada Nor dan dia tinggal bersama mereka. Suaminya mengatakan bahawa Bella telah kembali ke Amsterdam untuk berkahwin. Nor mengesyaki dan tidak lama kemudian anak-anaknya mula mempunyai kelakuan luar biasa. Anak pertama mereka suka bercakap dengan dirinya sendiri dan tidur di tempat yang rawak; suaminya menyembunyikan rahsia manakala seorang wanita tua sentiasa memberi amaran kepada Nor. Tanpa disedari oleh Nor, Bella yang hilang mungkin sedang mengintai di sudut gelap banglo itu.

Di sekeliling kawasan itu terdapat tembok gergasi untuk memastikan seluruh Detroit selamat. Bagi polis yang menyamar Damien Collier, setiap hari adalah perjuangan menentang rasuah ketika dia berjuang untuk membawa pembunuh bapanya, Tremaine, ke muka pengadilan. Sementara itu, Damien dan bekas penipu bernama Lino bekerjasama untuk menyelamatkan bandar itu daripada komplot untuk memusnahkannya.

programme.desc: Akil tidak lagi tahan dengan cerita orang-orang mengenai saka-saka yang berkeliaran di taman perumahan tempat Akil tinggal. Sebab itu jugalah dia bertengkar dengan kawan baiknya,Nabil. Akil panggil semua saka-saka dan memberi amaran supaya mereka pergi. Saka-saka itu enggan dan Akil cuba mendapat pertolongan pawang untuk menghalau saka-saka tersebut. Sedang pawang bermentera menghalau saka-saka itu, Sahak berlari menemui Pak Sudin di surau dan beritahu yang dia ternampak saka dekat rumahnya dan hantu-hantu itu dibela oleh Akil. Sahak sangat marahkan Akil. Cikgu Shila juga marahkan Akil dan semasa menemui Pak Sudin, Akil diberi nasihat supaya segera melepaskan saka-saka itu sebelum apa-apa perkara buruk berlaku. Akil memberi amaran supaya saka-saka-itu pergi dan kalau gagal, tahulah apa yang hendak di lakukannya.

programme.title: Check In Shock
programme.desc: Sekumpulan orang berkumpul di hospital terbiar untuk mengambil bahagian dalam rancangan realiti. Sesiapa yang berjaya bermalam di tempat yang dikatakan berhantu akan memenangi hadiah wang tunai. Apabila malam semakin larut, sesetengah daripada mereka mula mengesyaki bahawa penganjur tidak bercadang untuk membenarkan sesiapa pergi dengan ganjaran. Kebenaran ternyata lebih mengancam apabila roh yang menghantui tempat itu terbukti benar dan mula menyerang mereka.

programme.desc: Mengisahkan Hisyam yang menjaga bapanya yang mengalami masalah sering lupa. Kemudian, Hisyam menghidapi sejenis penyakit yang boleh membawa maut dan membuatkan bapanya pula mengambil alih tugas untuk menjaga Hisyam.

programme.desc: Faridah, pekerja warga asing terlibat dalam kes jenayah apabila telah menjadi saksi kes pembunuhan. Bertemu Hisham ketika cuba melarikan diri, mereka berdua mula jatuh cinta selepas menghabiskan masa bersama di kampung Hisham. Konflik berlaku apabila penjenayah tersilap menculik orang yang menyebabkan Faridah dan Hisham perlu melakukan sesuatu untuk menyelamatkan Azura.

programme.title: Anak Sarawak

programme.title: Estet
programme.desc: Mengisahkan para pekerja estet Cinta Manis yang bakal bertarung dengan kumpulan estet Red Cobra dalam satu perlawanan bola sepak yang sudah 20 tahun tidak diadakan. Farid dan Shashi, dua pekerja estet yang berkawan sejak kecil, menjadi harapan pekerja estet yang lain untuk menyelamatkan penindasan yang dilakukan oleh kerani estet, Pooniah. Seorang gadis cantik bernama Geetha tertarik hati dengan Farid dan Shashi. Sesi latihan dikendalikan oleh Subramaniam iaitu bapa Geetha yang dilantik sebagai jurulatih. Ayah kepada Shashi, Apaa, adalah pemain bola yang sangat mahir, tetapi telah berlaku insiden semasa perlawanan bola sepak estet itu dahulu yang mana kakinya patah diterjah oleh Junna, seorang samseng estet yang sengaja ingin menamatkan karier Apaa atas upahan Pooniah 20 tahun yang lalu. Berjayakah Farid dan Shashi serta kawan-kawannya membebaskan pekerja estet Cinta Manis daripada penindasan Pooniah?

programme.title: Siapa Tak Sayang Bini 2
programme.desc: Merupakan lanjutan daripada kisah dua keluarga yang ingin mengawal pasangan masing-masing. Kisah kali ini bermula apabila Saiful ternampak Karim yang sudah tidak takut isteri berjalan dengan seorang wanita muda bernama Sephia. Karim sering mendengar luahan Sephia yang sedang bergaduh dengan teman lelakinya. Saiful yang suka menyibuk itu memberitahu perkara tersebut kepada Kasmah, isteri Karim. Pelbagai kekalutan berlaku setelah Kasmah mengesyaki suaminya berlaku curang dan meminta bantuan Kamisah untuk menyiasat perkara ini. Dalam masa yang sama, Karim dengan bantuan Kassim mencari jalan untuk menjernihkan keadaan.

programme.title: Darah Satria

programme.title: Yang Berhormat
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Kuping, anak gelandangan yang menjalani kehidupan di Kuala Lumpur dengan melakukan pelbagai pekerjaan. Dia bersahabat dengan seorang OKU bernama Lobak dan Mat Yee. Pada suatu hari, Kuping terserempak dengan seorang lelaki bernama YB Salleh Ali dan terpesona melihat beliau memberi ceramah politik. programme.desc: Faridah, pekerja warga asing terlibat dalam kes jenayah apabila telah menjadi saksi kes pembunuhan. programme.title: Estet
programme.desc: Mengisahkan para pekerja estet Cinta Manis yang bakal bertarung dengan kumpulan estet Red Cobra dalam satu perlawanan bola sepak yang sudah 20 tahun tidak diadakan. Farid dan Shashi, dua pekerja estet yang berkawan sejak kecil, menjadi harapan pekerja estet yang lain untuk menyelamatkan penindasan yang dilakukan oleh kerani estet, Pooniah. Seorang gadis cantik bernama Geetha tertarik hati dengan Farid dan Shashi. Sesi latihan dikendalikan oleh Subramaniam iaitu bapa Geetha yang dilantik sebagai jurulatih. Ayah kepada Shashi, Apaa, adalah pemain bola yang sangat mahir, tetapi telah berlaku insiden semasa perlawanan bola sepak estet itu dahulu yang mana kakinya patah diterjah oleh Junna, seorang samseng estet yang sengaja ingin menamatkan karier Apaa atas upahan Pooniah 20 tahun yang lalu. Berjayakah Farid dan Shashi serta kawan-kawannya membebaskan pekerja estet Cinta Manis daripada penindasan Pooniah?

programme.title: Siapa Tak Sayang Bini 2
programme.desc: Merupakan lanjutan daripada kisah dua keluarga yang ingin mengawal pasangan masing-masing. Pelbagai kekalutan berlaku setelah Kasmah mengesyaki suaminya berlaku curang dan meminta bantuan Kamisah untuk menyiasat perkara ini. Dalam masa yang sama, Karim dengan bantuan Kassim mencari jalan untuk menjernihkan keadaan.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa (T) Ep223
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Reunion Dinner
programme.desc: Chao Yang and Zi Hong are soon to wed but both have not met the other's parents. When a client requests for a livestream of their reunion dinner to promote his products, it set the stage for their parents' first meeting. Estranged from his mother, Yang decides to rent a family for the dinner which results in a series of mishaps and hilarity.

programme.title: CZ12
programme.desc: Hawk leads a mercenary team to recover the bronze heads of the 12 Chinese zodiac animals, which were looted by foreigners in the 1800s. With a promise of a 10 times bonus by MP Corp if he can recover all of them, Hawk stops at nothing to accomplish the mission.

programme.title: Another Me
programme.desc: Constable Li Mao marries a rich girl but her parents disapprove of their marriage. One day, Li accidentally discovers that he looks exactly like the prince! While he aims to secure a high ranking position in the palace, the prince wants freedom, so they decide to switch identities. This however, got them both involved in the ministers conspiracy

programme.title: From Vegas to Macau III
programme.desc: Ken holds a wedding ceremony in Macau for his daughter Rainbow. However, an explosion during the wedding causes Rainbow to fall into coma, while Ken and his friend Mark, are accused of engulfing some illicit money. Enraged, Ken swears to seek vengeance and pursue the mastermind who has gotten them involved in his evil plan.

programme.title: Table for Six
programme.desc: In this comedy, three brothers reside in a home inherited from their late parents. The eldest brother insists they have dinner at home every night as a family, but tensions begin to rise when their girlfriends join in as well. Love, friendship, jealousy and complicated relationships are all on the menu for this table for six!

programme.title: Kung Fu Hustle
programme.desc: Mobster Sing aspires to join the Axe Gang. As he stumbles into a slum ruled by eccentric landlords that are kung fu masters in disguise, his actions cause the gang and the landlords to engage in an explosive kung fu battle

programme.title: VR Fighter
programme.desc: Bodyguard Long Wei has posttraumatic stress disorder after his wife's death. One day, he encounters Amy who works for a VR technology firm and is invited for a new product test. After the test, Long Wei becomes the firms VR fighter and dons the newly invented armour. However, as mysterious armed men break in, a fierce battle has just begun...

programme.title: The Monkey King 2
programme.desc: Monkey King is tasked with escorting Monk Tang on his journey to the West to retrieve the scriptures. During the trip, Monk Tang is being targeted by the seductive yet deadly White Bone Spirit, who feeds on the innocents to gain immortality. Monkey King will have to fight the White Bone Spirit in order to save Monk Tang!

programme.title: The Way We Dance
programme.desc: Tofu shop girl Fleur possesses a quirky gift for hip hop and dance which she uses to becomes a supernova in the university dance crew. Meanwhile, Alan, from the Tai Chi Club has an eye for Fleur's sleight of hand and tries to recruit her into his club.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Set in 2020 during the outbreak of COVID-19, the movie features interconnected stories of three women's lives as they navigate the uncertain future amongst their respective friends and families. From the struggles at home to challenges in relationships and conflicts at work, these three women rise with strength when faced with plights unknown.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon (2020)
programme.desc: In 1960s Hong Kong, rookie cop Xu Le cracks a robbery but gets demoted instead, as this offends a corrupt inspector. Xu meets a rich girl Bai who falls instantly in love with him one day. Will he break up with his childhood girlfriend for Bai so as to climb the social ladder, and how does Xu eventually become one of Hong Kongs legendary detective?

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: An emergency occurs on an offshore drilling rig that would cause it to capsize and sink. The Emergency Response Unit races against the clock in a chopper rescue mission amidst dangerous explosions and fire. Captain Gao Qian must work seamlessly with his chopper pilot Zhao Cheng to rescue survivors using the most maverick and dangerous tactics.

programme.title: Distinction
programme.desc: A music teacher in a special needs school, an underachiever from an elite school, and a rebellious teenager with a handicapped brother take part in a campus musical for various reasons. Little did they know that this turns out to be a journey of self-discovery.

programme.title: Kung Fu Hustle
programme.desc: Mobster Sing aspires to join the Axe Gang. As he stumbles into a slum ruled by eccentric landlords that are kung fu masters in disguise, his actions cause the gang and the landlords to engage in an explosive kung fu battle

programme.title: Princess and 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters live in Lucky Town, the only safe residing place in northeast China. When warlord Lam refuses to side with the Japanese, an agent is assigned to take over his army and kill his daughter using ninjutsu. Lams daughter escapes and seeks help from the seven masters, who finally defeat the enemy and save the warlord!

Chow Mo Wan encounters many women in his life but is touched by none after he lost his true love. Following an encounter one day, he decides to write a fiction titled 2046 which takes place at Room 2046. Nothing ever changes at Room 2046, and people go there to find their lost memories.

programme.title: Fist of Legend
programme.desc: When Chen Zhen studies in Japan, he finds several Chinese students missing and accidentally uncovers the Black Dragon Societys conspiracy. A new drug is invented to boost bodies of the Japanese troops in war and the Chinese students are used in their experiments. Chen Zhen vows to take down the evil society and destroy their secret laboratory.

programme.title: Mr & Mrs Gambler
programme.desc: Manfred and Flora are gambling addicts who have come across each other a few times at the casino, but do not leave impression on each other until they both suffer heavy losses and are held hostage by the loan sharks in Macau. They find themselves falling in love, and decide to get married when they come back to Hong Kong.

programme.title: Journey to the West: Conquering the Demons
programme.desc: The sequel to "Journey to the West: Conquering the Demons", this happens after Monkey King has gained enlightenment and is Tang San Zang's disciple. Tang, Monkey King, Sandy and Pigsy continue their journey to the West, where they have to fight and eliminate demons while dealing with their own changes, putting their bond to the test.

programme.title: Bounty Hunters
programme.desc: A group of bounty hunters, including San, Yo, Cat, Swan and Bobo, are tasked to track down the culprit of a series of bombings that have plagued an international hotel group. Unfortunately, Swan, Cat and Bobo are kidnapped by the mastermind of the bombings. Can San and Yo save them? Will the bounty hunters accomplish their mission?

programme.title: The Way We Are
programme.desc: Set in Tin Shui Wai, a marginalised satellite town, Kwai is a middle-aged widow who works hard in a neighbourhood supermarket to support herself and her son. They lead a mundane but fulfilling life. When an elderly woman who lives alone moved in to Tin Shui Wai, Kwai strikes up a friendship with her and helps her ease into a new life.

programme.title: Detective Chinatown 3
programme.desc: After the events in Bangkok and New York, Tang Ren and Qin Feng are invited to solve a murder case in Tokyo, but it turns out to be a challenge for the worlds best detectives. While the case has become complicated and confusing since the worlds top detective Q got involved, a hilarious challenge for the best detectives in Asia has just begun

programme.title: The Mask of Shura of Fire Cloud
programme.desc: 18 years ago, the evil Black Feather clan infiltrated the territory of Master Fire Cloud and stole The Mask of Shura, thus releasing an evil spirit that was a baby. Master Fire Cloud adopted the baby to prevent him from becoming evil. When the baby grows up, he takes control of the mask and becomes Fire Clouds successor as the citys guard.

programme.title: 72 Tenants of Prosperity
programme.desc: Ha Kung and Shek Kin are sworn brothers, but become sworn enemies in business and every aspect of life after Pinky, the girl they love, marries Ha Kung. It is only when the property owner of both their shops wants to terminate their tenancies forty years later, that they are able to resolve the rivalry.

programme.title: Ghost Wedding
programme.desc: Photographer Zhi Cheng is entangled with a "woman in red", leading to the deaths of his relatives one by one. When the girl he likes, Si Tong, also dies mysteriously, Zhi Cheng vows to find out the truth but ends up revealing the secret of a "ghost marriage"...

programme.title: L Storm
programme.desc: ICAC officer Luk and Chief Inspector Lau both hit a dead end when investigating their respective bribery and money laundering cases. When Luk is accused of bribery after being framed by the money launderers, he risks everything he has to find crucial evidence against them to clear his name.

programme.title: Divergence
programme.desc: Three men are going beyond what their jobs require them to do. An ill-fated police detective runs into a woman during his investigation on a money laundering case, a lawyer protects a corrupt businessman from law and a ruthless killer violates his code to get involved in a police investigation. These three men are thrown together by circumstance...

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xings son attempts drug trafficking to save his fathers studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: Journey to the West: Conquering the Demons
programme.desc: The sequel to "Journey to the West: Conquering the Demons", this happens after Monkey King has gained enlightenment and is Tang San Zang's disciple. Tang, Monkey King, Sandy and Pigsy continue their journey to the West, where they have to fight and eliminate demons while dealing with their own changes, putting their bond to the test.

programme.title: YUM Investigation
programme.desc: YUM is a detective agency that handles supernatural cases. As YUM investigates the evil spirits appearing in an old building, they discover that the spirits are created by a spirit master to haunt the residents so that the building can be vacated for redevelopment. Can the YUM investigators finally find ways to fight against the master?

programme.title: Moscow Mission
programme.desc: Based on the 1993 true event of the "China-Russia Train Robbery", a gang of criminals commits a heist, stealing cash and goods from the cross border train. A Chinese police officer disguises as a businessman takes charge of the operation to arrest the criminals, but uncovers a bigger conspiracy instead

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: When the Clouds Roll By
programme.desc: Su is a schizophrenic who refuses to believe that her pilot lover is killed in a plane crash and makes up stories to deal with things. She runs into an old classmate Lai, who is also a doctor one day, and he finds ways to treat her illness. Su slowly recovers and accepts the reality, as well as her newfound love.

programme.title: Challenge of the Masters
programme.desc: Young Wong Fei Hung must prove himself worthy to be taught by Master Lu, who was also his fathers martial arts teacher. Although he is defeated in a competition, Wong Fei Hungs passion in Kung Fu finally moves Lu and allows him to become Lus disciple.

programme.title: Return of the Phoenix
programme.desc: An imperial minister Cheng betroths his pretty younger daughter, Ye, to his friend's son, Mu. His wife however, refuses to let Ye marry before her elder daughter Yan, who is ugly and undesirable. Yan is asked to pretend as Ye to meet Mu but scares him away. A rich guy who likes Ye meanwhile pretends as Mu to attend the wedding...

programme.title: The Sword And The Lute
programme.desc: Gui Wu and his bride use the deadly weapon - Phoenix Lute to fight against evil, but the lute accidentally falls into the hands of bandits hoping to use it to take control of the province. Gui Wu must now fight to recover the lute and beat the bandits.

programme.title: Torrent Of Desire
programme.desc: Rich playboy David is a drunk until he falls in love with a fashion model Dan Feng and marries her. David's sister Mona is in love with his best friend Han Ming, who rejected her as he secretly loves Dan Feng as well. Out of jealousy and hatred, Mona lies to David about a fake affair between Han Ming and Dan Feng...

programme.title: Golden Swallow
programme.desc: A heroine finds herself in a love triangle with a swordsman and a warrior. They team up to conquer the evil forces of the martial arts world but she is unable to choose between both men even as they face a deadly duel.

programme.title: The Venus' Tear Diamond
programme.desc: Legendary rival jewel thieves Fragrant Night and Nocturnal Earl travel to Japan to steal the famous Venus Tear Diamond. They fall quickly in love at first sight, without knowing the other person is their rival and is after the same prize. Who will get the diamond, and will it mean the end of their new found love?

programme.title: The Kid With A Tattoo
programme.desc: Young Bao Tong witnesses the brutal murder of his kung fu master by a vicious villain. A large eagle tattoo on Baos chest was spotted by the killer as he escapes. Can Bao escape from the killer?

programme.title: Diary of a Lady-killer
programme.desc: Tycoon Zhou is a playboy who is engaged to be married, but that did not keep him from working his charms on as many ladies as he can. He keeps a diary about his romantic escapades and soon, the women with whom he has been intimate with are being murdered one by one. Zhou becomes the number one suspect by the police but is the killer someone else?

programme.title: The Imperial Swordsman
programme.desc: Fu is a government officer heading home after being charged with falsifying reports. En route, he encounters & recruits a skilled swordsman as a bodyguard. They then meet a fleeing bride and her maid who asked to join them for protection. When the group reach a ruined temple however, a gang of assassins appear and attack them

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: This is an epic tale set during the time of the Sino-Japanese war. A painter Yu saves a young girl, Lotus, who is being sold to a brothel. They fall in love, get married and settled in to a peaceful life. However, their life is soon shattered by the Japanese invasion and the brutal regime that follows.

programme.title: Brotherhood
programme.desc: Liu serves his triad society loyally and tries to live a respectable life, but over time his good intentions lead him to an all-out gang war with a startling conclusion.

programme.title: Lady Of The Law
programme.desc: Chan, the chief of Wan Sheng Escort, is forced to raise his opponents son, Yim. While Chan forbids Yim to practice martial arts, Yim secretly learns it. Ten years later, a rapist appears and Yim is arrested by a lady constable as the suspect. The rapist turns out to be Chans elder son and Yim is framed by the Chans. Can Yim prove his innocence?

programme.title: Na Cha the Great
programme.desc: Adapted from a chapter of the classic Chinese legend Investiture of the Gods, this is the story of Na Cha set 3000 years ago. After Na Cha sacrificed his life to save his parents, he is reincarnated with his spirit embodied in a lotus flower and is armed with two magic weapons to save the people from their despotic emperor.

programme.title: The Proud Twins
programme.desc: Jiang Xiao Yu is separated from his twin brother as a baby after his parents are murdered. He is taken by a couple to Villains Valley and raised to be a villain by a host of outlaws. Jiang leaves the valley to explore the world when he grows up. Will he be able to avenge his parents and meet with his twin brother?

programme.title: The Kingdom and the Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Cheng Te meets country maiden Li Feng on a visit to Southern China. It was love at first sight and the Emperor leaves with a promise that Li Feng would be his empress. When he sends for Li one year later, she was too ill to withstand the arduous journey and arrives just in time to die in the arms of her beloved...

programme.title: Men From The Gutter
programme.desc: Two very different cops are out to capture a local drug boss. In this sizzling crime thriller, the two cops go about doing their jobs differently - one does everything to the letter of the law and the other just doing whatever it takes to solve crime.

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: Zhang and Jins daughter, Peony, are betrothed at birth but Jin objects to the engagement now. Zhang meets a carp spirit that looks exactly like Peony and they fall in love. When Justice Bao is asked by Jin to distinguish Peony from her replica, he decides to quit the case when he witness the true love between Zhang and the carp spirit.

programme.title: Martial Arts of Shaolin
programme.desc: Zhi Ming, who trains at the Northern Shaolin Temple, teams up with Si Ma Yan, who trains at the Southern Shaolin Temple, to avenge both their fathers death by assassinating a corrupt magistrate, leading to a series of fierce battles!

programme.title: Melody of Love
programme.desc: Three young doctors pursue three hard-to-get beauties in this romantic film set in the 70s a-go-go era. They have no idea where to start and use Rock-paper-scissor method to match themselves with the girls. The tactics and tricks they use are hilarious and they have to reshuffle their plans when nothing leads to success!

programme.title: Shaolin Abbot
programme.desc: Monk Chi San is sent by his Shaolin Master to learn a special kung fu from a Wu Dang priest. He gets embroiled in the fight between the Qing and Ming camps and has to gather disciples to rebuild the burnt Shaolin temple at the same time.

programme.title: Love Parade
programme.desc: Fashion designer Shi asks his friend Mui to comment on his new design but is angered by her criticism. When Mui asks him to design a gown for her to attend a gala event, Shi takes revenge by making a clown costume instead. Seeing Muis embarrassment, Shi feels guilty and apologizes to her, before they fall in love

programme.title: Usurpers Of Emperor's Power
programme.desc: The last ruler of Tang, Li Yao is deposed by Chao Kuang-jun, the founder of the Sung Dynasty. Unfortunately his actions unleash a new plague - his brother Kuang-yi - on the courts and his people. The marauding Kuang-yi rapes and plunders. As more people get involved, it turns into a bloody battlefield of betrayal. It is up to upright officials like Li Lang to put an end to it. But can one man take on the imperial army?

programme.title: The Adventures of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung travels incognito to Jiangnan to review his peoples livelihood but soon discovers that corrupt officials are oppressing his people. The emperor meets an upright young man and they join hands to teach the corrupt officials a lesson. The young man was appointed as his bodyguard thereafter.

programme.title: The Spirit of the Sword
programme.desc: Water Clan Chief is severely wounded by a samurai killer shortly before the annual duel at Tai Lake. He sends his brother Bao Yu on a long journey to find an antidote for him. On the way, Bao Yu encounters Little Princess and falls in love with her, not knowing that she is hiding a secret plot

programme.title: The Merry Wife
programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. When they discover unwanted suitors going after their other halves, jealousy threatens to expose their marriage any minute!

programme.title: The Daredevils
programme.desc: Corrupt general Wang Li assumes power by killing his superior. The son of the murdered superior befriends four street performers called The Venoms, and they help him take revenge by posing as government officials offering a peace token to the corrupt general. When Wang arrives at a warehouse, he is ambushed by the Venoms!

programme.title: Young Lovers
programme.desc: Guitar-playing rich kid, Yang Fan, heads to Japan to join a rock 'n' roll band where he soon finds himself competing for the affections of two beautiful girls.

programme.title: Lion VS Lion
programme.desc: The traditional lion dance has never looked so good as in Lion VS Lion which captures the most impressive sequences of lion dancing on film. Besides being loaded with enjoyable martial arts chicanery, film historians can revel because it's also the first film that clearly demonstrates the intricacies and differences between the traditional Northern and Southern lion dancing techniques. The Five Venom alumnus and Chang Cheh discovery, Lo Meng, teams up with Liu Chia-liang protege Wang Yu, as they inadvertently turn from vagabond kung-fu school operators into anti-Ching, patriotic fighters.

programme.title: The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This side-splitting comedy sees naive Ah Niu headed to Hong Kong, where he is repeatedly exploited and taken advantage of, and eventually finds himself arrested and imprisoned! Can he survive difficult times and finally overcome adversity?

programme.title: Rivals of Kung Fu
programme.desc: Shen and Wong Fei Hungs relationship turns sour, and Shen frames Wong and his disciple for murder. They are saved by a businessman Zhou, but Wong must win the Lion Dance Trophy to return Zhous favour. Can Wong Fei Hung defeat all skilled martial artists and complete his mission?

programme.title: Carry on Doctors and Nurses
programme.desc: At St. Morant Hospital, a harried but lovely administrator must deal with lusty interns, student nurses, a delirious surgeon, a dissection fiend, a criticizing Commissioner and gross negligence at regular intervals! This comedy is based on the hugely successful British Carry On! film series.

programme.title: The Savage Five
programme.desc: A group of bandits flees with a stolen safe to a village where they oppress the villagers and force the blacksmith Wei to unlock the safe. Wei refuses and flees to report to officials, while heroes of the town emerge to fight the bandits.

programme.title: The Pearl Phoenix
programme.desc: In Huangmei Opera tradition, this movie tells the love story of Wen, who sells himself as a slave to a rich family, and Huo, the familys young daughter. The lovers are kept apart by Huos stepmother and Huo escapes by dressing up as a man. Wen is framed and put into jail so Huo has to go back and rescue her lover!

programme.title: King Cat
programme.desc: The son of the imperial teacher is beheaded by Justice Bao for corruption. Infuriated, the teacher hires assassins to kill Bao, who is saved by Zhan Zhao. Meanwhile, a royal treasure is stolen while a murder takes place. Bao is ordered to solve the case in ten days and Zhan quickly sets off to investigate. Will they solve the case in time?

programme.title: Jonah Hex
programme.desc: Oscar nominee Josh Brolin plays Jonah Hex, a scarred drifter and bounty hunter who can track down anyone...and anything. Having survived death, Jonah's violent history is steeped in myth and legend - leaving him with one foot in the natural world and one on the "other side." His only human connection is with Lilah (Transformers' Megan Fox), whose life in a brothel has left her with scars of her own. But Jonah's past is about to catch up with him when the U.S. military makes him an offer he can't refuse: in exchange for his freedom, he must track down and stop the dangerous terrorist Quentin Turnbull (Oscar nominee John Malkovich). But Turnbull, who is gathering an army and preparing to unleash Hell, is also Jonah's oldest enemy and will stop at nothing until Jonah is dead. Based on the legendary graphic novel, this epic adventure thriller gives a new face to the comic book genre by combining the Western genre with supernatural elements.

programme.title: Guardians of the Wild 2 - Big Move Ep1
programme.desc: The Lilayi Elephant Nursery near Lusaka in Zambia is home to four orphan elephants. The two oldest, four-year- olds Musolole and Zambezi, have been here since they were just a few months old. These boisterous babies are out-growing the nursery and its time to move to big school. Two hundred miles away, in the heart of Kafue National Park, lies elephant heaven - Camp Phoenix, the projects release facility, where older orphans are already adapting to life in the wild.

programme.title: Guardians of the Wild 2 - Zambia's Peaceful Primates Ep2
programme.desc: Kasanka National Park in Zambia is home to an unusual species of baboon. Kinda baboons have turned their backs on the aggressive displays of dominance usually associated with these large monkeys and lead altogether more peaceful lives. Living alongside one troop is a dedicated team of researchers whose mission it is to uncover these baboons secrets and understand what makes them who they are.

programme.title: Dew Drops Diaries Ep22
programme.desc: Tooth on the Loose / That Thing You Dew - When Phoebe convinces the Tooth Fairy to visit before Marcus has actually lost his tooth, the Dew Drops do everything in their power to make sure the tooth is out before she arrives! / The Dews decide to hold a concert in the park for their animal friends, but cant find the time to practice.

programme.title: Dragons: Rescue Riders Ep5
programme.desc: Heavy Metal - The Rescue Riders get stuck in a cave with their rival, Magnus, during a race to find a new source of an important mineral.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep1
programme.desc: King Me - Uncle King Julien abdicates his throne, handing off his crown to Prince Julien. Let the reign of King Julien the Thirteenth begin.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep2
programme.desc: Poll Position - King Julien learns that 99% of the lemurs love him, so he makes it his mission to find and convert his one "hater."

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep1
programme.desc: Lucky And The Unbreakable Spirit - A wild horse Spirit and a soontobe city girl Lucky become friends in a frontier town

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep2
programme.desc: Lucky And The Treacherous Trail - When Lucky gets wind of an advanced trail ride she decides to become the best frontier girl anyone has ever seen.overnight

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep16
programme.desc: Shark and Pilot Fish / Theo - When shark and pilot fish are separated its up to Kelp, Scallop, Cruz, and Waverly to help them find each other again. / Scallops friend Theo finally comes clean on why hes always rushing off.

programme.title: Dew Drops Diaries Ep24
programme.desc: Escape The Backpack / Play Date - While helping Lola pack for her first day of camp, the Dews get stuck inside her backpack! Using the random items inside, the Dews get crafty in their attempt to break out. / When Eden and Phoebe join Harper and Marcus for a playdate, the Dews disagree on what activity their kids should do, ultimately learning that there are lots of ways to play!

programme.title: Dawn Of The Croods Ep4
programme.desc: This Means Warts - When snobby neighbors move in next door and complain about a bone pile blocking their backyard view, The Croods launch into the first-ever prank war.

programme.title: Dawn Of The Croods Ep5
programme.desc: The First Picture Show - When Thunk invents the first-ever movie using shadow puppets, everyone in Ahhh! Valley loves it...until they are shocked by the ending.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep1
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and The Frenzied Farts of Flabby Flabulous - George and Harold create a comic book about their gym teacher, but after a freak accident turns fantasy into reality, the best friends must run from his revenge

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep2
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and The Dreadful Debacle of DJ Drowsy Drawers - George and Harold attempt to save the fun at their school dance, but matters are made worse when their music teachers transforms into the dull yet deadly villain DJ Drowsy Drawers

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep3
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and The Horrible Hostilities of the Homework Hydra - When George and Harold go back in time to stop the invention of homework, they realize they also eliminated the most important thing in the world: comic books

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep60
programme.desc: Sitting Ducks - Boss, Tina, JJ, Dez and Pip willfully get babysat by the Uncuddleables, planning to expose them as horrible sitters via secret, hidden cameras. But the plan is thrown for a loop when Tina's first night alone without her parents makes her fall for their sitter Mia as a "substitute mommy." Meanwhile, Nannycam uses the babysitting distraction to sneak into the Uncuddleables' secret garage hideout to gather intel with her own "B field team."

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep61
programme.desc: The Big Dumpling - The Uncuddleables have struck the Lil Dumpling baby pageant, replacing all of Baby Corp's super-cute top 5%er babies with not-cute bottom 5%ers. Boss, Tina and their field team race to caravan the 5%ers from their homes to the pageant before Nannycam deploys the nuclear option of unleashing the dangerously cute UBO on stage to salvage a Lil Dumpling win.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep62
programme.desc: The Great Medieval London Fire 1135 - Boss Baby and Tina reject the 5%er system that says the cuter you are, the more love you deserve. Teaming up with the Uncuddleables, the team tries to take down the system from within, forming a resistance of the eight department heads of Baby Corp in the hopes of changing the way we look at Baby Love forever.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep8
programme.desc: A Thread In The Dark - Klaus is injured and Verucas mage powers are not working, stifled by her time in prison. They encounter a dangerous village and Veruca reconnects with her abilities in time to save Klaus, but the two are soon captured by Po and Blade, who are unaware of Verucas rekindled powers.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep9
programme.desc: Slow Boat to England - Po and Blade head to the docks to take Klaus and Veruca to England, and Po tries to have fun with her on their last day together. However, Klaus and Veruca break free and hold Po hostage; Blade shockingly gives up the location of the fire whip to save him.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep10
programme.desc: The Knight's Fall Part 1 - Po and Blade rush to warn the Emperor about the weasels, but he has Po arrested and Colin captures Blade, revealing that she was never a knight. Thrown in a cell, Po reunites with Rukhmini and Mr. Ping, and he copes with the truth about Blade as they break out. Po fights Klaus and Veruca but is outmatched. Blade defeats Colin and hurries to help Po but is too late.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep1
programme.desc: A New Bergen-Ning / Laugh Out Cloud - Poppy throws a party to urge the Trolls and Bergens to build friendship When Troll Village has a drought Cloud Guy offers to wash away the problem after some quality time with Branch.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep2
programme.desc: Two Party System / Fun Branch - Poppy discovers that Branch and Bridgets birthdays are on the same day and throws them both partiesBranch attempts to prove to the Snack Pack that he is fun.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep3
programme.desc: Royal Review / Funishment - Poppy faces her first royal review as Queen and sets out to ensure 100 happiness in Troll VillagePoppy must figure out how to handle crime in Troll Village when Cooper steals a pie.
